snippet.title: Last few hours in INDIA🇮🇳 India to Dubai
snippet.description:
Spending my last few hours in India before flying back to Dubai… It’s always emotional to say goodbye to family, home, and memories. This vlog captures my final day in India, the packing, the goodbyes, and the journey back to Dubai. ❤️✈️

If you’ve ever lived abroad, you’ll relate to the feeling of leaving your hometown and returning to your life overseas. Watch my journey from India to Dubai and the emotional moments of leaving loved ones behind.

👉 Don’t forget to like, share & subscribe for more family vlogs, travel stories, and my life as a homemaker in Dubai.
